==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: cocks-eggs
<hw>cock's-eggs</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a weedy vine of Argentina
(<spn>Salpichroa organifolia</spn>) having solitary white flowers
followed by egg-shaped white or yellow fruit.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> cock's eggs, <spn>Salpichroa organifolia</spn>,
<spn>Salpichroa rhomboidea</spn>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cockshead</ent>⟦br⟧
